## Phase 2b Summary

All sprint-3 findings implemented and tests green.

### Findings Addressed in Phase 2b

FIND-401: Rust lib.rs — removed invoke_app_startup command and all DTOs; added
  settings_load/settings_save_impl helper functions; settings file at
  XDG_CONFIG_HOME (or ~/.config)/promptnotes/settings.json.

FIND-402: try_vault_path — replaced starts_with('/') with Path::new().is_absolute()
  for cross-platform absolute path validation.

FIND-403: AppShell.svelte — changed from aria-hidden/inert pattern to conditional
  rendering ({#if state === "Configured"} etc.) satisfying EARS spec literally.

FIND-404: Write authority — bootOrchestrator no longer calls setAppShellState.
  AppShell.svelte writes Loading before calling bootOrchestrator, applies
  routeResult.state after. effectful-isolation.test.ts ALLOWED_WRITERS updated.

FIND-405: tauriAdapter.ts — createTauriAdapter.invokeAppStartup() now calls
  runTsAppStartupPipeline() which orchestrates settings_load + fs_stat_dir +
  fs_list_markdown + fs_read_file IPC calls, pre-resolves async data, then runs
  pure runAppStartupPipeline with synchronous port adapters. PROP-002 exemption
  via @vcsdd-allow-brand-construction JSDoc comment.

FIND-406: VaultSetupModal.svelte — focus trap implemented with onMount capturing
  triggerElement (document.activeElement), initial focus set on first focusable
  element via Promise.resolve().then(), onDestroy restores focus.

FIND-407: VaultSetupModal.svelte — error banners only render when
  modalState.errorMessage !== undefined (removed ?? fallback defaults).

designTokens.ts — added CORRUPTED_BANNER_STYLES export (warnColor, border,
  borderRadius, fontSize, fontWeight) satisfying REQ-009 AppShell.svelte import.

